Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.49,Classroom,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H697481&\fscx48\fscy10\p1\pos(842.88,381.99)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
